<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Jupyter on 一塘</title><link>https://talengu.github.io/tags/jupyter/</link><description>Recent content in Jupyter on 一塘</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2017 16:00:04 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://talengu.github.io/tags/jupyter/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Jupyter notebook的配置</title><link>https://talengu.github.io/post/c7-toolchain/jupyter-notebook/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2017 16:00:04 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://talengu.github.io/post/c7-toolchain/jupyter-notebook/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>前言&lt;/strong>
本文介绍jupyter notebook的安装配置过程和实用技巧。
